## 🔧 **GitHub Integration** *(REQUIRED FOR PM-123)*

```yaml
github:
  # REQUIRED: Repository Settings
  default_repository: "your-org/your-repo"    # Your default repository for PM numbers
  owner: "your-username"                      # Your GitHub username

  # OPTIONAL: PM Number Configuration
  pm_numbers:
    prefix: "PM-"                            # Number prefix (PM-, TASK-, ISSUE-, etc.)
    start_number: 1                          # Starting number for new installs
    padding: 3                               # Zero-padding (3=001, 2=01, 1=1)

  # OPTIONAL: Integration Settings
  api_base: "https://api.github.com"         # GitHub API endpoint (rarely changed)
  default_labels: ["enhancement", "pm"]      # Default labels for new issues
```

**Configuration Instructions**:
- Replace `your-org/your-repo` with your actual GitHub repository
- Replace `your-username` with your GitHub username
- Customize PM number prefix if you prefer different format
- Add any default labels you want on new issues

